{"tid":1330601,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急］7月20唔好出去嘈，但記得要嗌陳伯佢哋行開吓","createTime":"2019-07-18T15:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T16:24:39.000Z","uid":147684,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1c251d3412e1c43ed63dae95e21c0a6626f1323c","tid":1330601,"uid":147684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:34:33.000Z","msg":"7月20預咗建制會放狗喺金鐘周圍咬，黑警一定唔會執法，亦唔好奢望守到啲memo紙，都無必要小學雞去奚落佢哋，大家休息吓準備星期日再出嚟好過，唔好浪費精力俾spotlight聽建制吠。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">但係！有無人知陳伯、梁伯、琳琳同埋其他絕食者會點？有無熟人知道最新消息分享吓？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n帶佢哋去海濱坐吓又好，返屋企休息一陣定去搵個地方傾吓偈都好，無必要留金鐘同狗互咬。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5f638c30df16aa5fae0eaba08d66dd281cd27e5","tid":1330601,"uid":147684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:36:35.000Z","msg":"自推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b57dd180428a18ac369ea26a878b7c66ce118ee1","tid":1330601,"uid":147684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c09ae4a73cb16d5e243dab2e4c97b55319fd2466","tid":1330601,"uid":147684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:50:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab71f01f69e7ee4e844d75c7a87c4fa7d29d16df","tid":1330601,"uid":274079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:54:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a082907bf347d4be531b73c377f591462290137c","tid":1330601,"uid":274079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:54:59.000Z","msg":"佢地已經付出左好多"},{"pid":"55ea864dc2e81fa5c8659f60f5d5bdc8563152c7","tid":1330601,"uid":274079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy"